of Lean Innovation.

62
00:03:17,516 --> 00:03:21,564
Lean innovation embraces
a philosophy of not letting

63
00:03:21,726 --> 00:03:24,483
perfection get
in the way of progress,

64
00:03:24,683 --> 00:03:26,126
as Tom Agan puts it.

65
00:03:26,326 --> 00:03:29,723
Lean innovation contrasts
conventional approaches

66
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:30,905
to product development,

67
00:03:31,105 --> 00:03:34,794
where R&D teams
expend enormous effort

68
00:03:34,994 --> 00:03:38,181
trying to create a perfected
multi-featured product

69
00:03:38,381 --> 00:03:39,986
over an extended period,

70
00:03:40,186 --> 00:03:44,155
without any sufficient actual
market customer or feedback.

71
00:03:44,355 --> 00:03:49,239
