too expensive, too complicated,

72
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:52,245
too different
from what customers want,

73
00:03:52,445 --> 00:03:53,633
and worst of all,

74
00:03:53,833 --> 00:03:56,031
too late to market.

75
00:03:57,574 --> 00:04:01,342
When thinking about lean innovation,
it is perhaps useful

76
00:04:01,511 --> 00:04:04,626
